  - image: {fileID: 0}
    h2Heading: 
    h3Heading: New Features
    bulletPoints:
    - Back-ported the refactored save system from the 1.2 upgrade dev repo
    - Added a HudHealthMeter for player health bar instead of counter
    text: 
    links: []
    highlightObjects: []
    actions: []
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    h2Heading: 
    h3Heading: Component Changes
    bulletPoints:
    - Changed the timing setup on ParticleToRigidbodyShellEject which might make
      the switch visible for slower shells
    - Changed the inspector properties for the FirstPersonCameraTransformConstraints
      which might affect people using it outside the expected first person body setup
